OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Falong the coast will spread inland
OL,7,Fthis evening driven by a moderate
OL,8,Fbreeze off the North Sea. Some fog
OL,9,Fpatches and spots of drizzle are
OL,10,Fpossible. Staying mild overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FRather cloudy to start, this
OL,13,Fclearing to give lengthy sunny spells.
OL,14,FCloud may linger near coasts. Warm or
OL,15,Fvery warm inland, cooler near coasts
OL,16,Fespecially in the breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
